var AVTransport = function (host, port) {
  this.name = 'AVTransport'
  this.host = host
  this.port = port || 1400
  this.controlURL = '/MediaRenderer/AVTransport/Control'
  this.eventSubURL = '/MediaRenderer/AVTransport/Event'
  this.SCPDURL = '/xml/AVTransport1.xml'
}
